Roadmap for LogDeck

------------
0.1 Features
------------

Stream Setup: Default text output (ostream)
LogLevel Setup: Default setup <time/datestamp>[LevelName]{Message}
Operation: Call log functions
Teardown: Housekeeping for default systems

------------
0.2 Features
------------

Stream Setup: User-defined/provided streams
LogLevel Setup: Custom datafields, user defined formatting?
Operation: Log utility functions (clear, new file, send log via email, etc)
Teardown: none

------------
0.3 Features
------------

Stream setup: generalize for database
LogLevel: Database logging schema setup?
Operation: database snapshots, reports, dynamic formatting
Teardown: persistent state

